FBIS4-62546 "drsov095_v_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-095 Daily Report 13 May 1994 Lithuania Plan Approved in Case of Nuclear Plant Accident Plan Approved in Case of Nuclear Plant Accident WS1605101294 Minsk BELAPAN in Belarusian 1300 GMT 13 May 94 WS1605101294 Minsk BELAPAN Belarusian BFN [Unattributed report: "Program for Building Communication Sites Was Adopted"] [Text] The Belarusian Cabinet of Ministers has approved a program for the building and upgrading of municipal facilities and roads in Braslav Rayon, Vitebsk Oblast, to provide for the safety of the population in case of an accident at the Ignalina nuclear power plant [Lithuania]. The program will be implemented in 1994-98.
